description:
TITAN

6" TITAN Safety Toe
Black Full-Grain Leather
  • Premium full-grain leather for comfort and abrasion resistance
  • Alloy safety toe shaped on women's TITAN last for lightweight protection and a roomy fit (26388 & 72399)
  • Cement construction for flexibility and reduced break-in time
  • 360 of lightweight comfort
  • Padded top collar for comfort
  • Molded polyurethane midsole for lightweight cushioning
  • Mesh lining with Agion antimicrobial treatment for odor control and comfortable feet
  • Cast metal top hooks for increased durability
  • Nylon diffusion shank for structural support and torsional rigidity
  • Contoured open-cell polyurethane footbed with Outlast Adaptive Comfort technology for breathable comfort and drier feet
Timberland PRO Rubber Outsole:
  • Low profile for high surface contact
  • Slip resistant
  • Oil resistant
  • Abrasion resistant
